## Architecture decisions log

| Decision | Chosen | Reason |
|---|---|---|
| Database | PostgreSQL | Relational fits, JSONB handles edge cases |
| Hosting | Supabase | Hosted Postgres, built-in dashboard, free tier |
| Court isolation | Court as universe separator | Kings and Nassau don't share data |
| Incident storage | Immutable raw narrative | Source of truth never overwritten |
| Case identifier | Internal ref + encrypted index | Pseudonymization without losing lookup ability |
| Sensitive fields | Encrypted at rest (`_enc` suffix) | Combination risk even on public data |
| Update pattern | Append-only | Full audit trail, nothing lost |
| Conflict handling | Store both sides, flag uncertainty | Don't resolve prematurely |
| Judge profiles | Factual + operational only | Defensible, useful, no editorial judgment |
| Judge profile categorization | observation_type field | Structures behavior by category not personality |
| Knowledge traceability | All lessons link to source incident | Every fact traceable to what taught it |
| PII in ingestion | Detect and pseudonymize before storage | Combination risk managed at entry point |

